  "1774860": {
    "name": "Plank Builders",
    "steam_appid": 1774860,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1774860/extras/7a613e5bf927dec28f55cf03847973ec.poster.avif?t=1734718640\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1774860/extras/7a613e5bf927dec28f55cf03847973ec.webm?t=1734718640\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1774860/extras/7a613e5bf927dec28f55cf03847973ec.mp4?t=1734718640\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏介绍</h2>探索一个充满魔力的奇妙世界，在这里魔法弹珠能让毛绒猴子活过来。携手这些生动有趣的小伙伴，开启一段激动人心的冒险旅程，用木板打造出令人惊叹的奇妙建筑。<br>踏上一场兴奋刺激的寻宝之旅，追踪并找到房间每个角落隐藏的毛绒小猴子。但可别忘了这里的特殊挑战——千万不要触碰地板！你需要策略性地铺设木板路径，建造日益复杂精妙的建筑，方能抵达每一只猴子的所在之处。<br>沉浸在《Plank Builders》宁静祥和的世界中，重拾童年的美好时光。尽情挥洒创意，唤醒所有小猴子，将整个房间打造成想象力的欢乐天地。<br><br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1774860/extras/3ca840a932b5fca03bb3f7263b6e71f4.avif?t=1734718640\" width=600 height=131 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >地板就是熔岩</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1774860/extras/436ff240930b4ae9fed7eb8a8afb10ed.poster.avif?t=1734718640\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1774860/extras/436ff240930b4ae9fed7eb8a8afb10ed.webm?t=1734718640\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1774860/extras/436ff240930b4ae9fed7eb8a8afb10ed.mp4?t=1734718640\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>只有在自己铺设的木板上才能安全行走。要想接触所有猴子，你需要精心设计并建造一系列结构，从简单构造开始，渐进到日益复杂的建筑。通过循序渐进的实践，你将掌握建筑艺术的精髓。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >赋予生命</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1774860/extras/036e5dc883ececf664ed4d5e2534e777.poster.avif?t=1734718640\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1774860/extras/036e5dc883ececf664ed4d5e2534e777.webm?t=1734718640\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1774860/extras/036e5dc883ececf664ed4d5e2534e777.mp4?t=1734718640\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>运用魔法弹珠的力量，唤醒更多猴子伙伴，让你的朋友圈不断扩大。感激你赋予生命，这些热心的小猴子会助你一臂之力，共同建造道路、桥梁和房屋等等。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >逼真物理</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1774860/extras/43f2f6f6db00c96bdcc188fc85f06671.poster.avif?t=1734718640\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1774860/extras/43f2f6f6db00c96bdcc188fc85f06671.webm?t=1734718640\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1774860/extras/43f2f6f6db00c96bdcc188fc85f06671.mp4?t=1734718640\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>游戏中的逼真物理效果会将你的建筑推向极限，为你带来不小挑战。你的精心杰作究竟能否迎接考验，还是终将屈服于重力法则？<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >技能提升</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1774860/extras/cf6b7c27f1a914385b7551ee01840b40.poster.avif?t=1734718640\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1774860/extras/cf6b7c27f1a914385b7551ee01840b40.webm?t=1734718640\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1774860/extras/cf6b7c27f1a914385b7551ee01840b40.mp4?t=1734718640\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>每唤醒一只猴子，你就能获得一个宝贵技能点。利用这些点数解锁崭新蓝图、升级和建筑技术。解锁热气球，在蓝天中自在翱翔。你能在高空发现更多隐藏的毛绒猴子吗？<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >建筑模板</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1774860/extras/b2664c5bb06b05c681f536b92ddf76c7.poster.avif?t=1734718640\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1774860/extras/b2664c5bb06b05c681f536b92ddf76c7.webm?t=1734718640\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1774860/extras/b2664c5bb06b05c681f536b92ddf76c7.mp4?t=1734718640\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>海量建筑模板作为自主创造的有力补充，助你实现心中宏伟蓝图。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >打造专属形象</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1774860/extras/baf8f44a98acec77f94f11536126cbb4.poster.avif?t=1734718640\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1774860/extras/baf8f44a98acec77f94f11536126cbb4.webm?t=1734718640\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1774860/extras/baf8f44a98acec77f94f11536126cbb4.mp4?t=1734718640\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>创造独一无二的“木板猴”，从颜色、发型到服装等广泛选项中自由搭配。尽情发挥想象，塑造彰显个人风格和创意的形象。",
